item.title: Simple-nano overview
item.description: Emacs package starter This repo can be used as the base for Emacs package development. It use Cask as the project management tool, also tests are included. travis-ci is enabled as the CI tool. coveralls is enabled as the coverage statistics tool. Don't use anywhere This Emacs package actually do nothing, be setup only with some nice tool and used as the base for development. And don,t use anywhere.
